name: Mycalculator
0:
”Alexa, ask my calculator to add 46 to 52.”
”Alexa, ask my calculator what is 2567 divided by 13”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my calculator
des: This allows users to perform simple arithmetic operations over an interaction with Alexa. The operations include simple addition, subtraction, multiplication and division on integers. Users can get answers with 1 line questions.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
